            "hide_image": false,
            "card_title": "Our Home Town Planet",
            "card_text": "We believe in RADICAL OPTIMISM and REAL CHANGE. We know we will never be perfect, but from day one, we’ve taken action with every package we develop. We’re mindful of our footprint and strive to minimize packaging while maximizing the use of recyclable and post-consumer recycled materials.",
